items.name: morpho
items.description: Morpho Blue is a noncustodial lending protocol for the EVM, offering flexible, efficient, and trustless lending markets. It enables permissionless market creation, oracle-agnostic pricing, and free flash loans, while remaining immutable and governance-minimized for seamless DeFi integration.
